sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Backend
        participant OMS as OMS
        participant Export as Order Export
        participant Glue as Glue Backend API
    end
    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External
        participant Talend as Talend ETL
        participant ERP as Plentymarkets ERP
    end

    Note over OMS: On order placement / state change
    OMS->>Export: Stage order + payments for export
    Note over Export: Scheduler triggers delta export every 10 min
    Export->>Glue: Provide order+payment delta
    Talend->>Glue: Pull/receive delta [REST]
    Talend->>ERP: Forward orders + payments
    ERP-->>Talend: Order-status updates
    Talend->>Glue: Inbound order-status delta
    Glue->>OMS: Apply order-status update
